eport\"/>\n* [[Liberty Counsel]] (2014, 2015, 2016, 2017, 2018)<ref name=\"LGBT\"/><ref name=\"2015Report\"/><ref name=\"2016Report\"/><ref name=\"2017AntiLGBT\"/><ref name=\"2019AnnualReport\"/>\n* [[MassResistance]] (2014, 2015, 2016, 2017, 2018)<ref name=\"LGBT\"/><ref name=\"2015Report\"/><ref name=\"2016Report\"/><ref name=\"2017AntiLGBT\"/><ref name=\"2019AnnualReport\"/>\n* [[Mission: America]] (2014, 2015, 2016, 2017, 2018)<ref name=\"LGBT\"/><ref name=\"2015Report\"/><ref name=\"2016Report\"/><ref name=\"2017AntiLGBT\"/><ref name=\"2019AnnualReport\"/>\n* [[Pacific Justice Institute]] (2014, 2015, 2016, 2017, 2018)<ref name=\"LGBT\"/><ref name=\"2015Report\"/><ref name=\"2016Report\"/><ref name=\"2017AntiLGBT\"/><ref name=\"2019AnnualReport\"/>\n* [[Parents Action League]] (2014)<ref name=\"LGBT\"/>\n* Pass the Salt Ministries (2014, 2015, 2016, 2017, 2018)<ref name=\"LGBT\"/><ref name=\"2015Report\"/><ref name=\"2016Report\"/><ref name=\"2017AntiLGBT\"/><ref name=\"2019AnnualReport\"/>\n* Pilgrims Covenant Church (2014, 2015, 2016, 2017, 2018)<ref name=\"LGBT\"/><ref name=\"2015Report\"/><ref name=\"2016Report\"/><ref name=\"2017AntiLGBT\"/><ref name=\"2019AnnualReport\"/>\n* Pray in Jesus Name Project, The (2014, 2015, 2016, 2017, 2018)<ref name=\"LGBT\"/><ref name=\"2015Report\"/><ref name=\"2016Report\"/><ref name=\"2017AntiLGBT\"/><ref name=\"2019AnnualReport\"/>\n* Probe Ministries (2014, 2015, 2016, 2017, 2018)<ref name=\"LGBT\"/><ref name=\"2015Report\"/><ref name=\"2016Report\"/><ref name=\"2017AntiLGBT\"/><ref name=\"2019AnnualReport\"/>\n* Providence Road Baptist Church (2014, 2015, 2016)<ref name=\"LGBT\"/><ref name=\"2015Report\"/><ref name=\"2016Report\"/>\n* [[Public Advocate of the United States]] (see [[Eugene Delgaudio]]) (2014, 2015, 2016, 2017, 2018)<ref name=\"LGBT\"/><ref name=\"2015Report\"/><ref name=\"2016Report\"/><ref name=\"2017AntiLGBT\"/><ref name=\"2019AnnualReport\"/>\n* [[Ruth Institute]] (2014, 2015, 2016, 2017, 2018)<ref n