-gay can refer to activities in certain categories (or combinations of categories): attitudes against or discrimination against LGBT people, [[violence against LGBT people]], [[LGBT rights opposition]] and [[LGBT matters and religion|religious opposition to homosexuality]].\n\nThe following groups have been listed as active anti-LGBT hate groups in the SPLC's annual reports (years in parentheses refer to the year in which the group is included):\n\n{{div col|colwidth=30em}}\n* [[Abiding Truth Ministries]] (2014, 2015, 2016, 2017, 2018)<ref name=\"LGBT\">{{cite web|url=http://www.splcenter.org/get-informed/intelligence-files/ideology/anti-gay/active_hate_groups|title=Active Anti-LGBT Groups|publisher=Southern Poverty Law Center|accessdate=July 9, 2014}}</ref><ref name=\"2015Report\"/><ref name=\"2016Report\"/><ref name=\"2017AntiLGBT\">[https://web.archive.org/web/20180408205201/https://www.splcenter.org/fighting-hate/extremist-files/ideology/anti-lgbt 2017 anti-LGBT hate groups], Southern Povety Law Center.</ref><ref name=\"2019AnnualReport\"/>\n* [[Alliance Defending Freedom]] (2016, 2017, 2018)<ref name=\"2016Report\"/><ref name=\"2017AntiLGBT\"/><ref name=\"2019AnnualReport\"/>\n* [[American College of Pediatricians]] (2014, 2015, 2016, 2017, 2018)<ref name=\"LGBT\"/><ref name=\"2015Report\"/><ref name=\"2016Report\"/><ref name=\"2017AntiLGBT\"/><ref name=\"2019AnnualReport\"/>\n* [[American Family Association]] (2014, 2015, 2016, 2017, 2018)<ref name=\"LGBT\"/><ref name=\"2015Report\"/><ref name=\"2016Report\"/><ref name=\"2017AntiLGBT\"/><ref name=\"2019AnnualReport\"/>\n* [[American Vision]] (2014, 2015, 2016, 2017, 2018)<ref name=\"LGBT\"/><ref name=\"2015Report\"/><ref name=\"2016Report\"/><ref name=\"2017AntiLGBT\"/><ref name=\"2019AnnualReport\"/>\n* [[Americans for Truth About Homosexuality]] (2014, 2015, 2016, 2017, 2018)<ref name=\"LGBT\"/><ref name=\"2015Report\"/><ref name=\"2016Report\"/><ref name=\"2017AntiLGBT\"/><ref name=\"2019AnnualReport\"/>\n*